          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A GPU with unified memory (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") is typically an integrated GPU. A GPU with dedicated memory (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/false",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") may take additional time to synchronize managed resources or copy data into private GPU resources.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
